Specifically the hybrids AA exp was bugged because it didn't factor in the fact hybrids gain exp faster than other classes. <br>
<br>
Hybrids were originally created with a Hybrid experience penalty. They needed more total experience to level than other &quot;pure&quot; classes. I don't recall the exact numbers off the top of my head but I believe hybrids needed about 35% more exp than the other classes. Later down the line Verant decided they didn't deserve this penalty so removed it.<br>
<br>
